    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear u... its just that i feel okay if i sit still, the pain only happens when i inhale deep. maybe i can just stay in bed for a few hours and see if the feeling passes? if it's just anxiety from the flight, wouldn't some deep breathing and a nap help more than rushing to a doctor?",
